==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: băichĭgāntóu gèng jìnyíbù
===Etymology===
Literally: Even a 100 foot stalk of bamboo can progress one more step.
===Proverb===
'''[[百尺竿頭]][[更]][[進一步]]'''
# Even though one has reached great heights of success, one should still strive to improve oneself.
===Alternate forms===
[[百尺竿头更进一步]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
